featuresDesc:
1. Toggle checkbox to enable or disable all collapsible section features globally;
2. Glob expressions (e.g., `docs/**/*.md`) to limit which files enable this feature. Supported syntax: `*` (any chars except `/`), `**` (any path), `?` (one char), `[abc]` (char class), `{a,b}` (alternation). Leave empty for all files;
3. Allow per-file control via frontmatter properties `collapsableSections` and `uncollapsableSections`. Supported values: "h1" | "h2" | "h3" | "h4" | "h5" | "h6" | "list" | "codeblock" | "table" | "plain_quote_block" | "callout".
